<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.10">
<l>vallā ḷilaṅkai malaṅkac caranturanta</l>
<l>villā ḷaṉaiviṭṭu cittaṉ viritta</l>
<l>collārnta vappūccip pāṭa livaipattum</l>
<l>vallārpōy vaikuntam maṉṉi yirupparē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten appūcci songs</l>
<l>that are full of the words expound by Viṭṭucittaṉ</l>
<l>about the master of the bow that shot arrows</l>
<l>in order to [bring] ruin to the strong man’s Laṅkā,</l>
<l>they will go and live permanently in Vaikunta.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
